Name: Sarah Johnson
Age: 32
Gender: Female
Occupation: Marketing Manager
Ethnicity: Caucasian
Past Medical History: Diagnosed with MS at age 28, no other significant medical history. Currently taking medication for MS and attends regular physical therapy sessions. No history of smoking or alcohol use.

Name: Sarah Johnson
Age: 35
Gender: Female
Occupation: Marketing Manager
Ethnicity: Caucasian
Past Medical History: Sarah was diagnosed with relapsing-remitting multiple sclerosis (RRMS) five years ago. She has experienced several relapses over the years, including numbness and tingling in her limbs, difficulty walking, and vision problems. She is currently taking a disease-modifying therapy (DMT) to manage her MS symptoms. She also has a history of migraines and occasional anxiety. Sarah does not smoke and drinks alcohol occasionally. She exercises regularly and follows a healthy diet.
